{"about_the_game":"Someone has summoned you to a new world, they want you to kill giant monsters and gather magic stones... For what purpose? As you try to survive, you find remnants of ancient wars and old gods...<br><br><u><strong>Walking platforms</strong></u><br>Upgrade your base to allow it to walk or even fly!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271150/extras/walk_5m.gif?t=1723890466\" /><br><br><u><strong>Giant bosses</strong></u><br>Some of these bosses can only be defeated with a base!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271150/extras/boss.gif?t=1723890466\" /><br><br><u><strong>Explore</strong></u><br>Take your time to explore the vast world of Loya!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271150/extras/procedural_5m.gif?t=1723890466\" /><br><br><u><strong>Towers</strong></u><br>Add defenses to your base by placing towers that automatically attack enemies<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271150/extras/towers_optim600.gif?t=1723890466\" /><br><br><u><strong>Building</strong></u><br>Collect resources to make your base!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271150/extras/build_optim600.gif?t=1723890466\" /><br><br><u><strong>Combat</strong></u><br>Choose from 4 distinct classes that you can unlock in the altar!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271150/extras/war_ult_optimize600.gif?t=1723890466\" /><br><br><u><strong>Energy</strong></u><br>Every machine in Loya needs energy to function. Use wind turbines and batteries to manage your energy supply. Be careful though, your base can only handle so much weight!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_ass